                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/714.]</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Minister</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-11-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 25, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Department approves the program as per your November 13, and authorizes the
                    necessary steps to carry out the recommendations in accordance with the demands
                    of the situation. The disposal of the naval forces is being discussed with the
                    Navy Department.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Knox.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
